title: Psychotronic Cinema # 1 - Frankenstein's Castle of Freaks

sources.title: PschotronicCinema1 FrankensteinsCastleOfFreaks
sources.description: Psychotronic Cinema is a program made in the spirit of old late night television movie show featuring some of wildest movies ever made. Frankensteins's Castle of Freaks: Count Frankenstein has been conducting experiments in an attempt to bring the dead back to life. When a caveman is discovered near the village and beaten to death by a mob of locals, Frankenstein acquires the caveman's body and brings it back to his lab where his life's work finally comes to fruition. The caveman lives again.
